Text:
Steve - happy birthday. Hope you’re having a wonderful day and all your birthday wishes come true. Make lots of memories.
Mary and David
Steve - happy birthday. Hope you have a great day. Make some memories. Dave
Thank you, I really appreciate it. 38 is going to be a great year.
Here are some pictures from the weekend. Melissa and I are making great memories together
Hello from St Pete and Happy Birthday. We came down for a couple days and had a great time. Flying back now. Enjoy your day
Thanks. Safe travels. Hope it’s not too hot in Fla

So much to be proud of. I remember her Day 1 at Villanova while we were just starting our stint at Hedgerow. 

I know Melissa cherishes your support, as do I. Thank you for being a great Dad, Grandfather, and father-in-law, among other great family titles. 

Here are two pictures I got at 6:30am this morning. She's not complete unless she's nursing others back to health. She has true purpose in this world and it's amazing to watch. 

You got this. Tomorrow will pass. We are saying prayers, but we both feel a peace about it. That said, you need anything, just say the word

Steve - thanks for sharing and the kind words.
I know the past few months have been challenging, but that to will pass. Stay focused on the important things in life and all will work itself out. Dave

Loved “Steve - thanks for sharing and the kind words.
